# The Great Chick-Chang Showdown

## Introduction

In a world where digital wallets reign supreme, the age-old debate of who holds the purse strings—guys or gals—still ignites curiosity. So, let’s dive into the numbers and see if the guys really do have more “Chick-Chang” than the gals!
